    "They then assessed \"phi-1's\" coding ability through the HumanEval test, which showed that \"phi-1\" outperformed other open-source models that were ten times larger and used a hundred times more data.",
    "This demonstrates that data quality can be more important than data quantity or model parameters.",
    "Microsoft suggested that just as a comprehensive, well-crafted textbook provides students with the necessary knowledge to master a new subject, high-quality data significantly enhances the proficiency of language models in code generation tasks (Gunasekar et al., 2023).",
